1. File system disk space usage
  df -hl
  -h: human readable
  -l: limit listing to local file systems
2. Estimate file space usage
  du -h -d1 /tmp
  -h: human readable
3. How to set alias
  1)Edit ~/.bashrc
    alias yourcommand="<<bash command expression>>"
  2) Edit ~/.profile 
    source ~/.bashrc
